Package: LODopt
Type: Package
Title: Cell Type Abundance Association Analysis for Single Cell Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Reuben", "Thomas", email = "reuben.thomas@gladstone.ucsf.edu", 
                  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Performs association analysis between cell type counts and 
    experimental conditions or phenotypes. Takes count matrices of cell types
    across samples and tests for associations with experimental design factors.
